tweet: Hi, I'm Dave and I'd like to say hello to anyone who wants to follow me and I will follow you back.
I'm a supplier of bamboo clothing in Nottingham and co-own Well Cultivated Ltd.   Thought introductions were needed so hello all.  Dave
Dropped daughter back off at Uni, just got back at 01:00am after 3 hours round trip (full up with Red Bull to keep my eyes on the road).
I've got 6000 bamboo hot towels arriving at Southampton tomorrow.  You can never have too much of a good thing !
Does anyone know that someone else owns www.twitter.co.uk and he gets 90000 or so hits per month......and he's not happy !
